_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":524454,"discussion_content":"要接受事物本来的样子呀","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1628239701,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":true,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"reply\":true,\"user_type\":2}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":298829,"user_name":"coder.js","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1338120,"ip_address":"","ucode":"3DE173A5D23690","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/14/6b/08/15c473ef.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624340892,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"18804210076","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"个人笔记<br><br>## 得失心<br><br>得失心会衍生出对失败的恐惧，进而影响发挥。<br><br>一旦你有了得失心，并且畏惧自己做得不好，担忧会浪费时间、带来失败的结果，你就迷失了。<br><br>&gt; 你越是担心某件事会发生，它就越可能发生。<br>&gt;<br>&gt; ———— 墨菲定律<br><br>## 工作记忆 &#47; RAM + CPU<br><br>工作记忆：在解决问题的时候，用于暂时存放信息和加工信息的记忆系统。 它的容量是有限的。<br><br>- 把所需的信息从长期记忆中提取出来<br>- 在 工作记忆中 进行存储、加工、处理，得到答案。<br><br>&gt; :whale: 相当于 RAM + CPU。<br><br>工作记忆能够存储和处理的信息容量越多，意味着你解决问题的能力就越强。<br><br>工作记忆 的容量是有限的，如果装了太多 忧虑，那结果也就忧虑了。<br><br>考试示例：做完这一题，再做下一题，做下一题时，忘记上一题。<br><br>## 如何超常发挥？<br><br>1. 把所有的得失心和前因后果都暂时忘掉。不设标准、不要焦虑，能做到怎样就做到怎样。<br>2. 尽量清理缓存，不要留恋先前做过的题目。做事情的时候，不要想；做完了，再去想。<br><br>## 犹豫不决<br><br>如果时常怀疑自己的方法是否正确，会占用了很多的工作记忆。<br><br>你不可能在一开始，就找到正确的学习方法。<br><br>必须接受这个事实：一开始的学习效率，必然不高。<br><br>虽然现在的方法不够好，但它可以经历的阶段性进步。<br><br>对于某一固定的学科或者领域，学习基本上是个匀加速或者变加速的过程，你的方法会逐渐完善，效率会逐步提高。<br><br>### 1 小时法<br><br>使用当前的方法，** 专 注 地 ** 学一个小时。然后根据实际情况做出改进，逐步迭代改进。<br><br>&gt; 专注很重要！！！<br>","like_count":4},{"had_liked":false,"id":298444,"user_name":"进化菌","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1276861,"ip_address":"","ucode":"B30A5F78BB4171","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/13/7b/bd/ccb37425.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624109902,"is_pvip":true,"discussion_count":1,"race_medal":5,"score":"18803979086","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"工作记忆有点像电脑的内存，真正能快速提取信息的容量总是有限的。<br><br>说到高考失利，我确实遇到过高考5年都没考好的，平时数一数二的成绩，终究是带上了魔咒。<br>于是，我倒是觉得与其让自己不去想那些有的没的，不如心里默念“我一定可以做到的”，想一想过往成功的经历，很快就能调整过来了~","like_count":4,"discussions":[{"author":{"id":2821728,"avatar":"","nickname":"600988292","note":"","ucode":"24BAE2B7A7B1E5","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"reply_author":{"id":0,"avatar":"","nickname":"","note":"","ucode":"","race_medal":0,"user_type":1,"is_pvip":false},"discussion":{"id":532078,"discussion_content":"默念的那一刻。你就“已经输了”","likes_number":0,"is_delete":false,"is_hidden":false,"ctime":1637508773,"is_liked":false,"can_delete":false,"is_complain":false,"is_top":false,"parent_id":0,"ip_address":""},"score":2,"extra":"{\"user_type\":1}","child_discussion_number":0,"child_discussions":[]}]},{"had_liked":false,"id":298325,"user_name":"冰雪巧克力🍫","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1021562,"ip_address":"","ucode":"91D97393C88C27","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/0f/96/7a/eba30193.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1624016540,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"18803885724","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"对，我也发现我后来读书时候没有以前那么沉浸和投入了。因为在意的多了，想记读书笔记，很容易注意力会转到记录格式上。注意力就跑走了。","like_count":4},{"had_liked":false,"id":298136,"user_name":"呵呵哒啦啦","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":2583106,"ip_address":"","ucode":"17C615078F8387","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/avatar/00/27/6a/42/ae1fb4c1.jpg","comment_is_top":false,"comment_ctime":1623921436,"is_pvip":false,"discussion_count":0,"race_medal":0,"score":"14508823324","product_id":100081501,"comment_content":"哈哈 我读到后面找到答案了","like_count":3},{"had_liked":false,"id":303324,"user_name":"赌神很低调","can_delete":false,"product_type":"c1","uid":1168545,"ip_address":"","ucode":"1066778E1EDF26","user_header":"https://static001.geekbang.org/account/ava